com.sterlingcommerce.activity

Interface ISCActivityConfig


  • public interface ISCActivityConfig
    This interface defines activity config object. Each ISCActivityTrackingInterceptor and ISCActivityTrackingProvider is supposed to return applicable configurations as this interface. asmishra

      • getId

        java.lang.String getId()
        Returns the id of the configuration. If two interceptors/providers provide two configurations with same id, one of them is ignored. id of the configuration
